data.description: Stop in for a tour of this charming home conveniently located in the heart of the Greenridge subdivision.  This 4-bedroom, 2- bathroom home was totally renovated in 2020. New owners have continued in the additions with many fabulous updates including a Briggs & Stratton Whole Home Generator, new kitchen appliances, and much more.  Other indoor features include: Updated Kitchen, Granite Countertops, new bathrooms, windows, AC, Flooring, Water Heater, Electrical Panel & Fixtures. New Water Softener, and the list goes on. Roof 2017. Outdoor lovers will enjoy the cozy front porch and oversized backyard. This is a must see.
